  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Teague\" title=\"House Teague\"><img alt=\"House Teague.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b0/House_Teague.svg/50px-House_Teague.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b0/House_Teague.svg/75px-House_Teague.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b0/House_Teague.svg/100px-House_Teague.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Hollis Teague</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Teague\" title=\"House Teague\"><img alt=\"House Teague.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b0/House_Teague.svg/50px-House_Teague.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b0/House_Teague.svg/75px-House_Teague.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b0/House_Teague.svg/100px-House_Teague.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nHollis Teague</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Rivers_and_the_Hills\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King of the Rivers and the Hills\">King of the Rivers and the Hills</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Predecessor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_II_Teague\" title=\"Humfrey II Teague\">Humfrey II Teague</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Heir</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tyler_Teague\" title=\"Tyler Teague\">Tyler Teague</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Successor</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tyler_Teague\" title=\"Tyler Teague\">Tyler Teague</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n~<a href=\"/index.php/Years_before_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_400_Before_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years before Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">400&#160;BC</a><br />at the <a href=\"/index.php/Teats\" title=\"Teats\">Teats</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Teague\" title=\"House Teague\">House Teague</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_I_Teague\" title=\"Humfrey I Teague\">Humfrey I Teague</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Hollis Teague</b> was one of the last monarchs of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Teague\" title=\"House Teague\">House Teague</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hollis_Teague&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Hollis was the second son of King <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_I_Teague\" title=\"Humfrey I Teague\">Humfrey I Teague</a>, who caused a massive uprising of riverlords by attempting to suppress worship of the <a href=\"/index.php/Old_gods\" title=\"Old gods\">old gods</a>. In the campaign's <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_Six_Kings\" title=\"Battle of Six Kings\">final battle</a>, Humfrey I perished. The crown passed on to Hollis' elder brother, <a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_II_Teague\" title=\"Humfrey II Teague\">Humfrey</a>, who was killed. Hollis picked up the crown and died in the battle, passing the crown to his younger brother, <a href=\"/index.php/Tyler_Teague\" title=\"Tyler Teague\">Tyler</a>, became king, only to be killed in turn. After Tyler's death, the princes' uncle, <a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Teague\" title=\"Damon Teague\">Damon</a> also picked up the crown but was killed. Thus House Teague became extinct.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hollis_Teague&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Torrence_Teague\" title=\"Torrence Teague\">Torrence</a><